1.What is NodeJs ?
--> NodeJs is the runtime environment for execute the javascript code outside of the web page.
--> NodeJs also set of built-in modules file system, networking and other susytem resource.
--> Using web services and API .
--> It was developed by GOOGLE.
--> In 2010 , the npm [NODE PACKAGE MANAGER] introduced , which made it easy for developers and reude of code.

